# Halyvernoxian App Models

This document defines the core data models for the Halyvernoxian app.

## Relationship Model
```dart
class Relationship {
  final String userGender; // "male" or "female"
  final DateTime userBirthday;
  final DateTime partnerBirthday;
  final DateTime anniversaryDate;
  final String userName;
  final String partnerName;
}
```

## Love Diary Models
```dart
class Memory {
  final String id;
  final String title;
  final String description;
  final DateTime date;
  final List<String> imageUrls;
}

class Milestone {
  final String id;
  final String title;
  final DateTime date;
  final int daysLeft;
  final String type; // "birthday", "anniversary", etc.
}
```

## Luggage Models
```dart
class Trip {
  final String id;
  final String title;
  final DateTime startDate;
  final DateTime endDate;
  final List<PackingItem> packingList;
}

class PackingItem {
  final String id;
  final String name;
  bool isPacked;
}
```

## Cartoon Generator Models
```dart
class Cartoon {
  final String id;
  final String description;
  final String imageUrl;
  final DateTime createdAt;
}
```

## User Profile Model
```dart
class UserProfile {
  final String name;
  final String partnerName;
  bool darkModeEnabled;
  bool notificationsEnabled;
}
```
